WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:05.500
Hello, Brian Bonds from Coral Ridge Presbyterian Church in Fort Lauderdale, Florida.

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:13.500
Just wanted to give a huge shout out to Melissa Gonzalez and her team from Enlace on setting us up at Monte de Oración...

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:19.500
...and having a great time with our mission group from Evangelism Explosion. We had 40 people in total.

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:24.000
We were able to spread out throughout the whole mountain.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:31.000
And she and her team gave us a wonderful experience of just getting to grow closer to God...

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:37.500
...set us up with a lot of different service projects and evangelism, outreach opportunities.

00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:43.000
It was a wonderful time for us and our team. We stayed for a week, and we really enjoyed our time there.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:48.300
We hope that you guys can have a similar experience to us, and if you have any questions, feel free to reach out. Thanks.
